<br>
Back in the day, Trakanon used to be a rotation mob on Cazic - the rotation started out as three guilds.  At the end, it was about 12 guilds long and people finally said &quot;screw it&quot; and he became FFA.  The rotation lasted a good year or so (mostly due to the fact that it was only three guilds most of that time) until people started figuring out that assuming no patches, they'd get a shot at Trak in about three months.  The rotation broke down as various guilds had no interest and as new guilds rose up in levels.  Now, Trak can be spawned for a couple of days before someone gets bored enough to put him out of his misery.<br>
<br>
What Verant needs to do is make Ragefire like Faydedar.  Just remove his loot (no more free CoFs) and make him a spawnable mob with an NPC on a five/eight hour timer. <p><body link="#FFFFFF" vlink="#CCCCCC">

